| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0514 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: dd9e6beb-9ca2-5cbd-9a59-803d8ba6f483"
